snippet.title: Eternights - Release Date Update Trailer
snippet.description:
The apocalypse arrives early! Eternights, is set to launch on PS5 & PS4 & Steam & Epic Store | September 12th 2023. 
Something has turned people into monsters, and it’s up to you to save the world… and your love life.
